The '''mini rail cannon''' was a powerful projectile weapon produced by [[Rika/Moab]] that was used by the [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[Solis]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It fired streams of superaccelerated metal that could destroy a combat droid with a single volley.

The cannon was used by Solis in the [[Crying Room]] where he liquidated six [[A-series assassin droid]]s and rescued [[Whie Malreaux/Legends|Whie Malreaux]] and [[Tallisibeth Enwandung-Esterhazy|Scout]] from [[Asajj Ventress/Legends|Asajj Ventress]].

